snippet.title: Gameplay Footage “Chica” | Five Nights at Freddy’s: In Real Time
snippet.description:
Real Time Studio is a Five Nights at Freddy's fan-game team. Join us on Gamejolt or watch us here on YouTube!


Real Time Studio:
​⁠@DIVIANSFM - Animation
​⁠@JAMESDEV535  - Game Development

Take a look at this in-engine gameplay footage of Five Nights at Freddy's: In Real Time, featuring Chica's Character Al, animations, and simulated sound effects.


Our collaborators form is up now! If you want to collaborate with us please fill out this form and we'll get back to you! https://forms.gle/gwyFvFYoLjzMkVRw7

Our social media links:
@RealTimeFNAF on all Platforms
(Instagram, Twitter, YouTube)

What is Five Nights at Freddy’s: In Real Time?
You work the nightshift at Freddy Fazbear's Pizza looking out for the animatronics, now moving towards you in real time. Relive FNAF 1 with a moving animatronics camera system; but as we all know, the animatronics tend to wander a bit. 

See you guys soon. 

Music:
Leon Riskin from FNAF World, Pizzeria Simulator and Sister Location.
Five Nights at Freddy’s by The Living Tombstone
Never Be Alone by Shadrow
Original Soundtrack by Taaryn C.
